{"article_id":"JulmAxM7hXcXdOYu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former FBI Director James Comey said","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he will return for more questioning on Capitol Hill later this month ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"as President Trump ripped into him","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"for apparently declining to answer certain questions on the advice of his attorneys during Friday ' s closed-door session .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Comey ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"who spent Friday testifying before House lawmakers ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"told reporters","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"his return visit will likely come the \" week after next . \"","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"In a tweet Friday night , Comey accused Republicans of desperation .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"`` Today wasn ' t a search for truth ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"but a desperate attempt","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"to find anything","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that can be used","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"to attack the institutions of justice","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"investigating this president , ''","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"`` They came up empty today","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"but will try again .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"In the long run , it 'll make no difference","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"because facts are stubborn things . ''","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Fox News is told","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"the second session with Comey could come Dec. 17 .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"He repeated his desire","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"for the testimony to be in an \" open setting , \"","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"but said","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"he would testify in private ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"as desired by House Republicans .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"A key focus of questioning from lawmakers ,","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Fox News is told ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"was Comey 's decision","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"to draft the 2016 statement","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"recommending against filing criminal charges in the Clinton email probe","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"before the former secretary of state was even interviewed ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"as well as the alleged political bias","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"demonstrated in a slew of text messages and leaks by top FBI officials .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Speaking to reporters ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Comey said","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"he ' s willing to continue testifying ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"even as he suggested","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"he didn ' t think","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"it was necessary .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" When you read the transcript ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"you will see","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"we are talking again about Hillary Clinton ' s emails , for heaven ' s sake ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"so I ' m not sure","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"we need to do this at all ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"but I ' m trying to respect the institution","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"and to answer questions in a respectful way , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Comey told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"\" You ' ll see","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"I did that in the transcript . \"","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"The committee is expected to release a transcript of the Comey interview as early as Saturday .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"LAWYERS STOPPING COMEY FROM ANSWERING QUESTIONS IN HILL TESTIMONY ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"ISSA SAYS","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"After Friday ' s session concluded ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"the president tore into Comey amid reports","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Comey ' s lawyers ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"including one from the Justice Department ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"have prevented him from answering a number of questions .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"\" It is being reported that Leakin ' James Comey was told by Department of Justice attorneys not to answer the most important questions , \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"\" Total bias and corruption at the highest levels of previous Administration .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Force him to answer the questions under oath ! \"","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Earlier Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"as the former FBI director was testifying ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Rep. Darrell Issa , R-Calif. , told reporters","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that some lawmakers have been frustrated with the testimony","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and that Comey didn ' t seem upset about being told by his lawyers","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"that he doesn ' t have to answer certain questions .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"`` One of the disappointments of this deposition so far has been the amount of times","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"in which the FBI believes","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"that Congress doesn ' t have a right","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to know , ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Issa said .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Issa said","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Comey has two attorneys ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"including one from the DOJ ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"who have \" instructed \" the former FBI director not to answer \" a great many questions","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that are clearly items at the core of our investigation. \"","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Issa said","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"the instructions have been followed with Comey ' s \" gleeful acceptance . \"","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"`` The Department of Justice is going to have to agree to allow him to come back","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and answer a great many questions","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"that currently he is not answering , ''","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Issa said .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Issa later told Fox News ' \" Outnumbered Overtime \"","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"that the questions","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"not being answered","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"generally concerned the Hillary Clinton email probe , surveillance warrants and the anti-Trump dossier .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Such hearings may not continue after the new year :","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"with Democrats taking back control of the House ,","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"would-be incoming House Judiciary Committee chairman Jerry Nadler , D-N.Y. , said Friday","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"he will end the GOP inquiry into DOJ and FBI actions during the 2016 election ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"calling it a waste of time .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Meanwhile , Comey on Friday offered praise for Trump ' s choice of William Barr ,","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"who led the Justice Department in the 1990s under then-President George H.W . Bush ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"to succeed Jeff Sessions as attorney general .","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"\" I like and respect Bill Barr , ''","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"`` I know","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"he ' s an institutionalist","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"who cares deeply about the integrity of the Justice Department . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":153,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":121,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":109,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":105,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":103,"right":104,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":106,"right":107,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nucl